# Firebase Functions Environment Configuration

## Required Environment Variables

Set these in Firebase Functions config:

```bash
# Gemini AI Configuration
firebase functions:config:set gemini.api_key="YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY"

# Judge0 Code Execution Configuration  
firebase functions:config:set judge0.api_key="YOUR_JUDGE0_API_KEY"
firebase functions:config:set judge0.api_host="judge0-ce.p.rapidapi.com"
```

## Deployment Commands

```bash
# Install dependencies
cd functions
npm install

# Deploy functions
firebase deploy --only functions

# Deploy hosting + functions
firebase deploy
```

## Environment Variables Needed:
- `gemini.api_key`: Your Google Gemini API key
- `judge0.api_key`: Your Judge0 RapidAPI key
- `judge0.api_host`: Judge0 API host (default: judge0-ce.p.rapidapi.com)
